<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.279002>
    dc:description "FIGURES 39 – 44. Discepholcia, Tambana, Xanthomanthis, adults and male genitalia. 39 – Discepholcia caerulea, male, Thailand (AP); 40 – Tambana variegata, male, Vietnam (GR); 41 – Xanthomantis cornelia, male, South Korea (NIAST); 42 – Discepholcia caerulea, male genitalia, China, genit. prep. HHL- 1767 - 1 (NEFU); 43 – Tambana variegata, male genitalia, Vietnam, genit. prep. 378 Speidel (WS); 44 – Xanthomantis cornelia, male genitalia, South Korea, genit. prep. 94 - 1 (NIAST)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/279002/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.279008>
    dc:description "FIGURES 67 – 71. Trisuloides and Disepholcia, female genitalia. 67 – T. sericea, North India, genit. Prep. Z 4219 GB; 68 – T. rotundipennis, South Korea, genit. prep. HHL- 480 a- 2; 69 – T. becheri, China, genit. prep. HHL- 1508 - 2; 70 – Discepholcia caerulea, China, genit. prep. HHL- 1766 - 2; 71 – Xanthomantis cornelia, Russia, Primorye terr., 1295 IBP." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/279008/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

